%h2 Money Trail

.grid_12.alpha
  %h2 Contributions
  - if @person.has_contributions?
    .small.quiet.grid_24
      Data provided by the non-partisan <a href="http://www.followthemoney.org/">Follow The Money</a>. Read more <a href="http://www.followthemoney.org/Institute/about_data.phtml">about the data</a>.
    %div.grid_4.alpha
      %h3
        By Industry
      - @person.industry_contributions.each do |c|
        .grid_3.alpha
          = c.name
        .grid_1.omega
          = number_to_currency(c.amount)

    %div.grid_4
      %h3
        By Sector
      - @person.sector_contributions.each do |c|
        .grid_3.alpha
          = c.name
        .grid_1.omega
          = number_to_currency(c.amount)

    %div.grid_4.omega
      %h3
        By Business
      - @person.business_contributions.each do |c|
        .grid_3.alpha
          = c.name
        .grid_1.omega
          = number_to_currency(c.amount)

  - else
    .grid_12.alpha
      No data is available for this Member at this time via FollowTheMoney.org. To inquire how you can help make this info available and ensure transparency in government, visit
      %a{:href => 'http://www.followthemoney.org/Contact/index.phtml?dvd=8'} here
      == .
